OL,5,G0100 Outback Truckers
OL,6,     FHouse mover Robbie MacKay is
OL,7,     Fdragging a house up a mountain and
OL,8,     Flong-haul drivers Mish Aladin and
OL,9,     FDrew Norman are trapped by rising
OL,10,     Ffloodwaters.
OL,11,G0200 Trucking Hell
OL,12,     FWhen Storm Isha hits
OL,13,     FNorthumberland, Mouse attempts a
OL,14,     Fdangerous rescue in high winds;
OL,15,     FMick saves a dustcart from
OL,16,     Ftoppling over and Steve hauls a
OL,17,     Ffully loaded tanker out of the
OL,18,     Fmud.
